txt.en: Angmarim enemies perform rituals in the camp of Mullach Cagar. They must be defeated.
You have defeated many Angmarim in Mullach Cagar.\n\nYou should return to Molkha.
The Angmarim camp of Mullach Cagar lies south of Fellgát.\n\nYou should defeat Angmarim in Mullach Cagar.

'While you are investigating Mullach Cagar, I know Hórin will want you to defeat as many of the Angmarim stationed there as you can. We do not know what they are up to, but I guarantee you it is not in our best interests to let it continue!\n\n'Put an end to their evil and it will benefit the Gabil'akkâ, [placeholder]!'
'I knew you could handle them on your own! Good work, [placeholder].'
